data.description: A stunning waterfront home that combines luxurious living with exceptional outdoor amenities. This magnificent property provides space for relaxation and entertainment. Move-in ready with more to offer than any new home. Step inside and be greeted by the features that make this property special. Working from home is made easy with an office, providing a private and quiet space for productivity.  Car enthusiasts will appreciate the three-car garage along with the garage door located in the back that allows easy access to the boathouse and back deck. One of the highlights of this home is the 28-foot boathouse with boat lift and additional lift for small boat or jet ski, complete with a top sun deck that offers breathtaking views of the surrounding waterfront. Has 22kw generator, providing peace of mind during power outages and no flood insurance required.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this waterfront property that seamlessly blends comfort, functionality, and outdoor recreation.
